msgstr ""
"o usando la combinazione di tasti <keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>H</keycap>."

#: src/toolbox/transform/handle-transform.xml:173(para)
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>Shift</keycap> and click on a handle to <emphasis>move</"
